snippet.title: KOAKUMA | Closed Beta Version 2 ⚔️
snippet.description:
In October 2022, Koakuma CBT2 will launch 💫 

We've made a full range of updates from Randomized Dungeon, Skill Upgrades ⚔️ & High-quality graphics 🤩

You'll able to challenge more bosses in dungeons🎪#Koakuma #web3 #CBT2
